Class NameUsageSolrSearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.api.model.checklistbank.search.NameUsageSearchResult
      • org.gbif.checklistbank.index.model.NameUsageSolrSearchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.gbif.api.model.common.LinneanClassification, org.gbif.api.model.common.LinneanClassificationKeys

    public class NameUsageSolrSearchResult
extends org.gbif.api.model.checklistbank.search.NameUsageSearchResult
    This class contains the annotations required by SearchService and the Solr result/object mapping. The intention of having a separate class containing mostly annotations is to avoid the usage of specific Solr annotations in the model objects that are part of the API. Scoring used in this class: canonical_name:Abies^100 scientific_name:Abies^10 scientific_name:*Abies*^0.2 vernacular_name:Abies^25 vernacular_name:Abies^6 vernacular_name:*Abies*^0.2 kingdom:Abies phylum:Abies class:Abies order:Abies family:Abies^2 genus:Abies^2 subgenus:Abies^3 species:Abies^5 description:Abies^0.3
